---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Me - Rugved Katole"
  description="PhD candidate at The Ohio State University specializing in robotics, world foundation models, and Vision-Language-Action systems."
>
  <Navigation />

  <main class="about">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about__header">
        <h1 class="about__title">About Me</h1>
        <div class="about__divider"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="about__content">
        <section class="about__bio">
          <h2 class="section-title">Who I Am</h2>
          <p class="bio-text">
            I'm Rugved Katole, a PhD candidate in Computer Science at The Ohio State University (expected 2029),
            with a BE in Mechanical Engineering from BITS Pilani. A robotics enthusiast at heart, I've spent 4+ years
            bridging hardware and AI to create autonomous systems that make real-world impact—from precision agriculture
            to wildlife conservation.
          </p>
          <p class="bio-text">
            As a Graduate Research Associate at OSU, I pioneer techniques in world foundation models and Vision-Language-Action
            (VLA) systems to tackle data scarcity in robotics. This includes augmenting video datasets for faster inference
            (5.9× speedup) and building NVIDIA Omniverse-based digital twins for simulating animal behaviors, enabling ecologists
            to test drone algorithms virtually before deployment. Previously at IIT Bombay's TIH Foundation and ARMS Lab,
            I led deployments in autonomous navigation and multi-agent planning.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="about__projects-highlight">
          <h2 class="section-title">What I've Built</h2>
          <div class="projects-list">
            <div class="project-item">
              <h3>Autonomous Vineyard Rover</h3>
              <p>Integrated segmentation neural networks and depth sensing for lane centering on uneven terrain, handling up to 40° slips—deployed in real vineyards for data collection.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="project-item">
              <h3>Multi-Agent RL Framework</h3>
              <p>Combined CNNs to cut field scouting needs by 60%, slashing labor costs 4.8× and boosting farmer profits 36%, with 80% accuracy.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="project-item">
              <h3>Decentralized AV Intersection Manager</h3>
              <p>Graph-based system for communication-free, deadlock-free navigation across 255 scenarios, using road-marking intent detection.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="project-item">
              <h3>Distributed Patrol Algorithm</h3>
              <p>Scalable trajectories balancing priority sites, with sim-to-real validation for security patrols.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="project-item">
              <h3>Swarm Synergy Algorithm</h3>
              <p>Communication-free community formations, tested in multi-robot labs.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="bio-text">
            I've also spearheaded a $100K research grant, mentored students, and taught ROS 2 courses to advance the robotics community.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="about__cta-section">
          <h2 class="section-title">Let's Connect</h2>
          <p class="cta-description">
            I'm always interested in discussing research collaborations, speaking opportunities,
            or consulting on AI and robotics projects. Best way to reach me is through Email or LinkedIn.
          </p>

          <div class="cta-buttons">
            <a href="mailto:katole.2@buckeyemail.osu.edu" class="btn btn--primary">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"></path>
                <polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"></polyline>
              </svg>
              Email Me
            </a>
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/rugved-katole" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn--secondary">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                <path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433c-1.144 0-2.063-.926-2.063-2.065 0-1.138.92-2.063 2.063-2.063 1.14 0 2.064.925 2.064 2.063 0 1.139-.925 2.065-2.064 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/>
              </svg>
              Connect on LinkedIn
            </a>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="about__interests">
          <h2 class="section-title">Technical Expertise</h2>
          <div class="interests-grid">
            <div class="interest-card">
              <h3>AI & Foundation Models</h3>
              <p>Vision-Language-Action models, synthetic data generation, world modeling, deep learning, computer vision (PyTorch, TensorFlow, JAX)</p>
            </div>
            <div class="interest-card">
              <h3>Robotics Systems</h3>
              <p>Control systems, SLAM, motion/behavior planning, sim-to-real transfer (ROS 2, Gazebo, CARLA, Isaac Sim, MATLAB/Simulink)</p>
            </div>
            <div class="interest-card">
              <h3>Programming & Tools</h3>
              <p>C/C++, Python, Linux, Git/CI-CD, containerization (Docker, Singularity), Slurm for HPC</p>
            </div>
            <div class="interest-card">
              <h3>Leadership & Communication</h3>
              <p>Cross-functional collaboration, technical leadership, critical thinking, problem-solving, grant writing, mentoring</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about {
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: 6rem 0 4rem;
    background: var(--color-white);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .about__header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .about__title {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-black);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .about__divider {
    width: 80px;
    height: 4px;
    background: var(--color-black);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about__content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-black);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .bio-text {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .bio-text:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .about__projects-highlight {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .projects-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .project-item {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--color-gray-100);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-gray-200);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .project-item:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-black);
    transform: translateX(4px);
  }

  .project-item h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-black);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .project-item p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .about__cta-section {
    background: var(--color-gray-100);
    padding: 3rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    border: 2px solid var(--color-gray-200);
  }

  .cta-description {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 0.375rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    border: 2px solid transparent;
  }

  .btn svg {
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .btn--primary {
    background: var(--color-black);
    color: var(--color-white);
    border-color: var(--color-black);
  }

  .btn--primary:hover {
    background: var(--color-gray-800);
    border-color: var(--color-gray-800);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  }

  .btn--secondary {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--color-black);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-black);
  }

  .btn--secondary:hover {
    background: var(--color-black);
    color: var(--color-white);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .interests-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .interest-card {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--color-white);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-gray-200);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .interest-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-black);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .interest-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-black);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .interest-card p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .interests-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    .cta-buttons {
      justify-content: flex-start;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about {
      padding: 5rem 0 3rem;
    }

    .about__title {
      font-size: 2.25rem;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .bio-text {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .about__cta-section {
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .cta-buttons {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .btn {
      width: 100%;
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }
</style>
